OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTom Kerridge: Catering is  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fan uphill struggle now     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Since Covid, there hasn't been any     
OL,6, respite for the hospitality industry,  
OL,7, says celebrity chef Tom Kerridge. For  
OL,8, his TV series he has been going behind 
OL,9, the scenes at pubs and restaurants     
OL,10, across the UK, as the industry he knows
OL,11, and loves is hit by a tidal wave of    
OL,12, rising costs.                          
OL,14,F"There hasn't been any positivity or   
OL,15,Fgood news in three or four years," says
OL,16,FTom Kerridge. "Every day feels like    
OL,17,Fyou're walking uphill, on glass,       
OL,18,Fbarefoot."                             
